## Labels

There is a way to display labels for the Heatmap items. If `label.enabled` is set to `true`, the labels will show a numeric value from `colorKey`.

```js
colorKey: 'temperature',
label: {
    enabled: true,
},
```

A label formatter can be used to customise the labels.

```js
colorKey: 'temperature',
label: {
    enabled: true,
    formatter: ({ datum, colorKey }) => {
        const value = datum[colorKey];
        return `${value.toFixed(0)}Â°C`;
    },
},
```

